Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:32.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.33,0:01:35.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.95,0:01:40.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白白的  好漂亮  像雪一般
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.56,0:01:45.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰都不撿嗎  那來我家吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.03,0:01:51.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真漂亮  給媽媽看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.10,0:01:56.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.47,0:02:00.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行  男子漢不能動不動就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.05,0:02:03.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後要獨自生活了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.89,0:02:14.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  塔子阿姨
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.30,0:02:17.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心  玩得開心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.31,0:02:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:20.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.01,0:02:22.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.78,0:02:27.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為教學合宿要去雁羽溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.42,0:02:29.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.09,0:02:35.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  要讓您出合宿的費用
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.03,0:02:39.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事不用在意
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.27,0:02:42.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點事想拜託你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.01,0:02:48.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能到溫泉附近的窯戶去幫我取茶碗嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.49,0:02:52.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來聯絡說是馬上就能做好了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.95,0:02:55.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能拜託你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.48,0:02:59.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然了  滋叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:07.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑得真嚇人  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.65,0:03:13.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  你什麼時候…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.10,0:03:17.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保鏢跟去是理所當然的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.47,0:03:18.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這麼高興
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.51,0:03:30.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受人所託去做事  當然是很高興的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.63,0:03:49.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「強梁霸道終殄滅  恰似風前塵土揚」
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.29,0:03:55.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的  上午的課就上到這裡  午飯前是自由活動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.58,0:04:01.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  接下來去做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.57,0:04:03.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然先去泡溫泉啦  溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:04.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.03,0:04:08.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我還有點重要的事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.15,0:04:11.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:18.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.78,0:04:21.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概就在附近了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.91,0:04:24.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.31,0:04:32.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,膽小鬼小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.52,0:04:41.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在森林亂竄啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.13,0:04:44.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物很礙眼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.09,0:04:53.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快滾出森林  廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.95,0:04:56.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢物？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:58.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫你滾出去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.98,0:05:01.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.35,0:05:07.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.20,0:05:12.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做什麼  欺負這麼小的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.65,0:05:16.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.44,0:05:20.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類竟敢小看我們  不知天高地厚
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我吃了你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.33,0:05:52.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.62,0:06:01.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是一樣愛管閒事啊  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.87,0:06:04.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:10.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但這次可算是白來了  還得再過來一次
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.76,0:06:15.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒辦法嘛  茶碗要明天才能做好嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.57,0:06:19.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是麻煩的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.68,0:06:25.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是放食物的容器  在附近的超市買就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.89,0:06:28.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說就太直截了當了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.59,0:06:30.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體不是容器吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.53,0:06:31.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.20,0:06:32.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我討厭人類
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:32.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然還是容器嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.41,0:06:33.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs40\an8\fad(0,300)}（注：貓咪老師把俗語作字面理解了,「沒有身體和蓋子」）
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.85,0:06:33.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  要過去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.13,0:06:37.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了  來了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.25,0:06:39.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:46.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  別睡覺
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:53.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.36,0:07:09.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才我被丟向夏目的粉筆打中了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.79,0:07:12.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.93,0:07:17.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚飯會是什麼呢  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.49,0:07:19.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  真期待啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.18,0:07:24.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目總是笑著  但總覺得不真實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:31.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,語言和姿勢  連氣息…也覺得不真實
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.44,0:07:44.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或許他並不是人類
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.17,0:07:51.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是跟我一樣化為人形獨自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:56.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  跟我一起住在這森林就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.05,0:07:59.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧  母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.72,0:08:16.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,頭疼了  明天就要回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.61,0:08:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過於親近的話他就太可憐了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.26,0:08:20.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.20,0:08:23.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.00,0:09:02.38,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真倒霉
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.50,0:09:05.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣根本沒法去取茶碗啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.23,0:09:08.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上課前能不能趕回去都是問題
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:12.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:18.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.50,0:09:44.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,母親大人  我也能幫助別人了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他跟我說「謝謝你了」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.97,0:10:06.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是沒用的人了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.56,0:10:11.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天去摘蘑菇  摘很多很多  分給夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:19.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲  小狐狸  你還賴在這裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.90,0:10:22.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不長記性的傢伙  說了叫你滾的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.43,0:10:35.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這森林不需要你這種廢物
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.74,0:10:39.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  我不再是廢物了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.78,0:10:42.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪裡不是…好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.18,0:10:42.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.44,0:10:49.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的小子  不可原諒…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.16,0:10:57.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說過叫你們住手的了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.79,0:10:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.92,0:11:02.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨天的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.35,0:11:08.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只用拳頭還不夠嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.56,0:11:11.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目大人  夏目大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.47,0:11:13.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.69,0:11:16.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您忘記了嗎  夏目玲子大人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.20,0:11:22.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是說過到春天就將名字還給我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.08,0:11:26.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的玲子  又幹這種罪孽深重的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:28.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春天？這是第幾個春天了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.01,0:11:34.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫我的就是你嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.19,0:11:37.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  茶碗拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:47.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  早蕨  這是你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.55,0:11:55.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:11:58.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個友人帳的主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.62,0:12:02.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我確實收到了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.85,0:12:07.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,友人帳？我聽說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.08,0:12:11.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被寫下名字的就會以主僕之契建立關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.83,0:12:14.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會被奪走名字的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.52,0:12:17.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.73,0:12:19.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.94,0:12:24.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛才歸還了名字  怎麼會去奪取名字呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:30.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫了我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請讓我做你的手下
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.05,0:12:34.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會起到作用的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:37.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要啦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.91,0:12:46.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我很軟弱嗎  我沒用嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:50.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想用這種東西來互相束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.55,0:12:54.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是主人跟手下的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.50,0:12:57.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:03.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得我們擁有其他的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.16,0:13:17.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,顏色真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.32,0:13:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去換衣服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.59,0:13:23.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朋友介紹給我一處好窯戶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.13,0:13:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為家族增加了  就借機訂一套
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:33.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的份  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.68,0:13:36.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝您了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.88,0:13:40.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像小狐狸說的那樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.83,0:13:42.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事  夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.29,0:13:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有沒有用的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.86,0:13:48.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼  完全不明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:13:58.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然很漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.92,0:14:03.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想給夏目也看看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.03,0:14:08.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目…我想見夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.29,0:14:14.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子漢不能動不動就哭
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:18.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我決定要變強  總有一天能幫上夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.09,0:14:25.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼想見夏目嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.62,0:14:28.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽過傳言了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.11,0:14:34.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像認識那個擁有友人帳的夏目嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.17,0:14:39.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能完全化作人類嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.64,0:14:41.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:49.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能讓我吃魚吃個飽  就告訴你能跟夏目見面的方法吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.37,0:15:14.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣…你能告訴我跟夏目見面的方法了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.72,0:15:23.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨狐狸  你被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:27.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就因為你這麼笨  才會總是孤單一人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.33,0:15:31.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目早就忘記你了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.37,0:15:39.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收下吧  小狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.45,0:15:43.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能變成人類一天的藥
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.86,0:15:46.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變成人類的藥？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.27,0:15:51.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見面只要自己去見就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.70,0:15:53.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.24,0:16:00.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  只要去見他就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.59,0:16:26.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了  我好歹也是狐狸
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.31,0:16:30.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要去人類的世界  就能追尋夏目的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:33.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我走了  母親大人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:56.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目一個人有沒有寂寞呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.93,0:17:14.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目的氣味
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.92,0:17:29.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  夏目的氣味…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.62,0:17:44.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想見他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.32,0:17:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目  你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.26,0:17:53.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.00,0:17:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  你沒事吧  一個人嗎  媽媽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.51,0:17:58.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一個人沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.47,0:18:06.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想見他  好想見他
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.82,0:18:08.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪裡  夏目在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.11,0:18:11.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.81,0:18:14.51,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.57,0:18:15.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快啦  快啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.47,0:18:17.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.19,0:18:19.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是夏目啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.87,0:18:20.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大豐收嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.25,0:18:22.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.09,0:18:28.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.72,0:18:36.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏目的氣味  在這裡  就在這附近
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.01,0:18:37.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能見面了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.72,0:19:07.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做好了哦  貴志釣的真鱒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.97,0:19:11.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是條好真鱒  開動了  貴志
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.60,0:19:12.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.68,0:19:14.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,貴志能吃河魚吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.13,0:19:16.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  我都能吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.21,0:19:19.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃的東西要說出來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.69,0:19:24.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滋他不吃青椒  像小孩子一樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:28.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我小時候也不吃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.37,0:19:31.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  有同伴了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.65,0:19:35.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:42.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塔子  這真鱒非常好吃哦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.02,0:19:45.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我也嘗一口吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.56,0:19:46.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請吧請吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.99,0:19:48.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.97,0:19:55.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  很好吃  能吃到這麼美味的東西真開心
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.20,0:20:06.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  夏目看起來很高興
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.20,0:20:08.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本不寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.27,0:20:14.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寂寞的…寂寞的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:23.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.74,0:20:31.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:34.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是那時的小狐狸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.55,0:20:38.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你  特地來見我的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.91,0:21:16.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可愛的帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:19.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃完飯一起回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:26.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得記住路啊  下次我去見你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.61,0:21:31.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.76,0:21:42.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.83,0:21:48.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算寂寞也不敢邁出腳步  沒想過去做點什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.98,0:21:54.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以或許很多東西就無法察覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.07,0:23:50.09,biaoti1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(140,550)}虛幻之光
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.75,0:23:37.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人能看見妖怪
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.73,0:23:40.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與之交心  終於成為了重要的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.73,0:23:41.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:43.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,變得無法看見妖怪了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.79,0:23:46.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果那個人能幸福  我就沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.15,0:23:49.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎  清


